---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
	<main class="p-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
		<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-800 mb-4">AURA Protocol</h1>
		<p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
			Attribution & Usage Reporting for AI. A transparent and structured approach to disclose AI-assisted content creation.
		</p>

		<p class="text-gray-600">
			AURA establishes a protocol for authors, developers, and publishers to embed verifiable metadata describing AI involvement in digital content. The protocol supports transparency, reproducibility, and traceable contribution reporting in scientific, creative, and technical domains.
		</p>
	</main>
</Layout>
